{"id": "cc4e26620d0a3358ea4b3724f91160346306b89da97be2541b823611254111ac", "item_id": "5314035cd6:0", "text": "Using your own OCIO config"}
{"id": "b54c889d409623c6c629d03b8cd9501814f7c64acb73859d1104b8bb0a32387a", "item_id": "5314035cd6:1", "text": "OCIO Roles"}
{"id": "eec48728cc72e4cedaca98567c7bb99f6ae22d0fb6590e2329d626c518a22883", "item_id": "5314035cd6:2", "text": "RenderMan relies on a few OpenColorIO roles that need to be defined in your"}
{"id": "2f589f5c15b667fdb64e50f832baa8dd46b193a35a3728b35af7dd0829ae4e96", "item_id": "5314035cd6:3", "text": "config.ocio"}
{"id": "eb36be6c06717c3b88700bdc0678576b33b6b4ef76de644a43b56023e9e77cb0", "item_id": "5314035cd6:4", "text": "file."}
{"id": "f748f8d90516c1cecee83006e3c9de6c9117affdf9c6e42e0b450195ed88bac8", "item_id": "5314035cd6:5", "text": "rendering"}
{"id": "839aa262c99212b215198a5af4b08157c5245602b5067e2cb3e7636d4b1d85c5", "item_id": "5314035cd6:15", "text": "MANDATORY"}
{"id": "51c234952553a586e46acd085540590ce6a80b302ce5dbb6ab68431985f4532e", "item_id": "5314035cd6:8", "text": "This is the space in which all computations are done by the renderer."}
{"id": "3a6eb0790f39ac87c94f3856b2dd2c5d110e6811602261a9a923d3bb23adc8b7", "item_id": "5314035cd6:9", "text": "data"}
{"id": "335fd665f279a081079a603243547268742c8e8d0af2f06b6a4b09b40c06e243", "item_id": "5314035cd6:11", "text": "STANDARD"}
{"id": "c0838a7a4315e3139655f03b4994ec04aeb9d1a422f3dc30769aefb008ec2b77", "item_id": "5314035cd6:12", "text": "An input that doesn't need to be converted because it provides numerical data (normal map, bump map, roughness map, etc)."}
{"id": "103292fd580eeb9fca8fbe49e53abf0d9f55703bb77d36ae4f2e84636f301704", "item_id": "5314035cd6:13", "text": "srgb_linear"}
{"id": "002e5f550b0886f9aa055c85a5a7172faeeebfe84e95715948a9061d33a374e6", "item_id": "5314035cd6:16", "text": "A linear sRGB/Rec.709 image, like an HDRI environment map."}
{"id": "ec6bb80ab97691e7a66f230832be2ccb75e6169c04a1fd2ca72abf289ff6cb37", "item_id": "5314035cd6:17", "text": "srgb_texture"}
{"id": "a1ecfbc428c56381d461525feb3ea8adbe5da8a74af7937d151c9ffe9a092534", "item_id": "5314035cd6:19", "text": "A non-linear sRGB image, like a JPEG, PNG, etc."}
{"id": "bde7ca36dd5b4e90634b05b603b46406b4cdff97b0015fd0262b80ba80d11ecc", "item_id": "5314035cd6:20", "text": "This role has been added to our basic linear configuration and to the Filmic-Blender configuration."}
{"id": "deff4c6e59141cf644bb48f40becbef63f8192c4303119cace5fc3a3c284b14d", "item_id": "5314035cd6:21", "text": "In ACES-1.2, this is already an alias to"}
{"id": "c02f6af743f44edf6e57bcbbd5c37ab08ec1793c847982ff8217c479fcc6362f", "item_id": "5314035cd6:22", "text": "Utility - sRGB - Texture"}
{"id": "eaaaf41ae0b29991e448ee0bb9929ab54ac95d02a894c2f1fbb5cd40c8c3772d", "item_id": "5314035cd6:24", "text": "In practice, these 4 roles will be what most people need to effectively use colour-management. Still it is possible to add more role through the JSON configuration file."}
{"id": "d3ed1ebc2d93becddd8c8236cb27b0f8569f29f712dd9e6cc6e906247fc30611", "item_id": "5314035cd6:25", "text": "JSON Configuration file"}
{"id": "fe8d9bd46668c68fa82b4d503772a782d63e4f2867ae087e2b67ae40d7c69acb", "item_id": "5314035cd6:26", "text": "Many configurations contains a large number of color spaces, for special cases that are not related to 3D rendering. The only things that matter to 3D artists boil down to a handful of controls."}
{"id": "07739bcdc3a076d7b33e415c449d0ff6f2d53a5902613b6398464f11644e6053", "item_id": "5314035cd6:27", "text": "In order to provide a central configuration point, RenderMan requires a JSON configuration file to provide:"}
{"id": "2b3fd0d6fc4eaf2d36eea17ca38c7b49e6501d5345b5bd96a5e90bea4595f8b9", "item_id": "5314035cd6:28", "text": "A list of Roles/ColorSpaces available in UI controls."}
{"id": "7a759a4404cfb38af32f9dd98df7402c4a640e02249ced39d38800d29a988279", "item_id": "5314035cd6:29", "text": "A list of aliases (shortened forms) that will be inserted in texture names to disambiguate them."}
{"id": "4f9e8fbf07a01c9ffa2ee151da9bd206dce0fc5fec4aef01453b46d7dd0d3e59", "item_id": "5314035cd6:30", "text": "A list of help strings that can be displayed in the UI controls."}
{"id": "1de0749e19b82231060e6199b097d5e420bcca2daeeb9702f225e7e4aac22249", "item_id": "5314035cd6:31", "text": "A set of rules for the Texture Manager to assign initial txmake settings."}
{"id": "3efed3de9d4b5170f223c8abdeaafa7e9a9b8884ca0886bd44c6d3c3e72d4766", "item_id": "5314035cd6:32", "text": "File name"}
{"id": "c553971513acbe1bb1fe1f0e027c7de6ec011a7d62e9acd2920bb955e8f49e55", "item_id": "5314035cd6:33", "text": "The JSON file's name is based on the directory containing the"}
{"id": "430473329df5ca205e93d09d202c021d973044142fe20fc4abf555135c405c44", "item_id": "5314035cd6:34", "text": "file:"}
{"id": "f9862ff69c30a71c468cc36f7cf77b6f0da21ee65307a3b0be50b110fdfb9af1", "item_id": "5314035cd6:35", "text": "File location"}
{"id": "4321d6549eb7736b81777a23faf0f61c8908f687d2849ef495fa86cdd5235935", "item_id": "5314035cd6:36", "text": "At startup, the files in"}
{"id": "3d8b184383961d4552e819a936d43da099a8b3c5006386db58bb274c6970188e", "item_id": "5314035cd6:37", "text": "will always be read."}
{"id": "8a86cf4a9810ec60037c53ad06babdaee7ea2a3a02b96357a2d86cf519d2894f", "item_id": "5314035cd6:38", "text": "If the"}
{"id": "4bd471a2fe1ec5182378fe983fac32462fd8d44aac6351936b6607d6f16098d5", "item_id": "5314035cd6:39", "text": "environment variable is defined, all files matching the"}
{"id": "28b2f1435950e328fba36c4fe21279b57f6bda1571af2160cd1d909ead4dcc44", "item_id": "5314035cd6:40", "text": "pattern in that directory will be loaded. This mechanism can be used to override stock configurations or add support for a custom OpenColorIO configuration."}
{"id": "2583d8b2a301aae132b292e5395485130a9ca5b73fdf6a4362efe29cc3a88534", "item_id": "5314035cd6:41", "text": "Sample file"}
{"id": "b3b18cd57ec548fd622d6dd522bf5c74bbefdae8bf7a13ec17d5233d0545653d", "item_id": "5314035cd6:42", "text": "rman_color_config_ACES-1.2.json"}
{"id": "4228aeb07c410ffc9d15b458bf7c2bf8d9dfa7af632f2c339e69f8cb54654da3", "item_id": "5314035cd6:43", "text": "Rules"}
{"id": "d44b27e50263f615789bba956da0c29552d5f476854d805f01bc27e566e2bf15", "item_id": "5314035cd6:44", "text": "Rules allow the Texture Manager to set reasonnable conversion defaults to newly referenced images. If done well, it fully automates texture conversion."}
{"id": "7160c938eadbca34034afe6da22dbbd7fc7c61a28dc62cc495a1fc5e7d922d4f", "item_id": "5314035cd6:45", "text": "Rules are defined by node types: pattern, light, lightfilter and imageplane. This allows you to specialize conversion without relying on a complex set of rules."}
{"id": "090772cf4068973daad3f715eb788d39fe2c02be42efd86de81f0e59198d6237", "item_id": "5314035cd6:46", "text": "args"}
{"id": "8a3ed3afe0993ac3257224602608e7fc00202abe897054d21afb0399b5f48ff4", "item_id": "5314035cd6:47", "text": "This is a dictionnary of txmake flags with their value to define a baseline that can be modified by rules."}
{"id": "3c014c66178eb16ddca075c4a7a57d06b5c216644fea20e3d3cb29b4fc7000fe", "item_id": "5314035cd6:48", "text": "Rules with a"}
{"id": "74234e98afe7498fb5daf1f36ac2d78acc339464f950703b8c019892f982b90b", "item_id": "5314035cd6:49", "text": "null"}
{"id": "6f3fc4698929c75c944969b1fde88ff39b51fbc3da90f3499fcacd97b3ffeb98", "item_id": "5314035cd6:50", "text": "value are disabled."}
{"id": "f0f89300f311bb59e5d7328a12a95722290b9451fc1383145a0a2ca1c8d7af2e", "item_id": "5314035cd6:51", "text": "texture_type"}
{"id": "031d9b6b8a4c6e5c642206c3e12c0aa782a4ece807221badf6979263b4f4c708", "item_id": "5314035cd6:52", "text": "\"regular\" for generic textures or \"envlatl\" for environment light textures"}
{"id": "1d8ed937b50fcad6d5f2bb2fffbfba172818a79e65179ee1e7e0c8dda82463d5", "item_id": "5314035cd6:53", "text": "texture_format"}
{"id": "f12f09e55f1e9836a1042e0e5f00e06916256ec1910b89143b766712de70df19", "item_id": "5314035cd6:54", "text": "The file format of the texture: \"pixar\", \"tiff\", \"openexr\""}
{"id": "acd532d8913e66d436b38de9acba750f92f20e16c49dafb78b69363127a38c60", "item_id": "5314035cd6:55", "text": "resize"}
{"id": "13995dcb32b6a8b38bd624e6001abc7b3071126879568a022f22fe30f7d57da6", "item_id": "5314035cd6:56", "text": "Resize image to a power of 2 using given mode: \"none\", \"up\", \"up-\", \"down\", \"down-\", \"round\", \"round-\"."}
{"id": "d0172eb5edb9133219774052c16459574bd5dfb4c697edbafcf675cc1386acfc", "item_id": "5314035cd6:57", "text": "texture_filter"}
{"id": "8fd5ed3aada8380f50deb15f27c7a63a8adfb85e62b27cad8f40354623509466", "item_id": "5314035cd6:58", "text": "Filter used for resize: \"point\", \"box\", \"triangle\", \"sinc\", \"gaussian\", \"gaussian-soft\", \"catmull-rom\", \"mitchell\", \"cubic\", \"lanczos\", \"bessel\", \"blackman-harris\""}
{"id": "d683610083e6d6dddad8e78b00ed28242e87b963ff308c545fd3492a12e873ec", "item_id": "5314035cd6:59", "text": "smode"}
{"id": "12d988cfa362f39992f8a311631c36fee4a500b7771b8c67af4a310e242a9a17", "item_id": "5314035cd6:60", "text": "Repeat mode in s direction: \"black\", \"clamp\", \"periodic\""}
{"id": "2029b9560ac3c43b5d1ba7a4dee97b078d2dc90cf557ecf1636e55bf8d2cde97", "item_id": "5314035cd6:61", "text": "tmode"}
{"id": "dbdc704c9faa09ac4f840f5f4490ed18be893333e53bcec6d095ba2b665bdcff", "item_id": "5314035cd6:62", "text": "Repeat mode in t direction: \"black\", \"clamp\", \"periodic\""}
{"id": "1f6d8a95b4cacbe5781080aa58c29bd62b97d85bd86e29c76484b852b8ca05e6", "item_id": "5314035cd6:63", "text": "data_type"}
{"id": "1eca6860e13898328f444e4ac058147cac34a4d7fad67d4629667298953f24b6", "item_id": "5314035cd6:64", "text": "\"float\" (float 32), \"half\" (float 16), \"byte\" (int 8), \"short\" (int 16)"}
{"id": "d18f849bb8c5ffef9e1b9b8719e3bcbba35f100655be40f035aeace790dec16b", "item_id": "5314035cd6:65", "text": "compression"}
{"id": "d27bc91a0cd07164e324552556d2e8254661f1d58585f852b7eef485be131533", "item_id": "5314035cd6:66", "text": "Compression used on texture tiles to save disk space. Texture fomat dependend: see txmake help."}
{"id": "9c2d7dd7d906f5009762b006c707798948247163b3b6657a0a615979340b307e", "item_id": "5314035cd6:67", "text": "compression_level"}
{"id": "081997501cd46b1e93c07b02cf59877e695774e9a9228b657dc79aad22584ae5", "item_id": "5314035cd6:68", "text": "Compression level for compressors supporting that parameter: see txmake help."}
{"id": "ba20236679dd1d114e7ee424a47b6f2b372e19c6a3fe137ace223fa5420703ba", "item_id": "5314035cd6:69", "text": "ociocolorspace"}
{"id": "035a5b20542f350760ffc683b41986250c3296313fd7f8ec02f93d6e5894de96", "item_id": "5314035cd6:70", "text": "The destination colorspace, that is the colorspace of the texture"}
{"id": "e4020274573cd1cbba6f79fee9c936b61e4f6778c034417c3a099ad6dbde750a", "item_id": "5314035cd6:71", "text": "ocioconvert"}
{"id": "78abe5f5522904decd8e8fb7475dfdb6299f0491f14710e165be80ffddf3e1c0", "item_id": "5314035cd6:72", "text": "The source colorspace, that is the colorspace of the image"}
{"id": "4ba3eaee655c353a79b534463a6a7fe444e3a4dc3c8ac46452b7aab1c337eca7", "item_id": "5314035cd6:73", "text": "ociodither"}
{"id": "6aa05e046932e55fd2acb76d8128779392a36b885b70f6f5094120e5f1dac18d", "item_id": "5314035cd6:74", "text": "Optionaly dither pixel values when outputing to a non-float texture format. Not recommended."}
{"id": "450109693211a3fe70ad0c3a97babcc96e362f439c8d56fe014de0d05c95e5bb", "item_id": "5314035cd6:75", "text": "bumprough"}
{"id": "9fbd4cf046519e3c67dfb83b4e2ebcb321d44c9ec74f8e89067e098ecc9ea28f", "item_id": "5314035cd6:76", "text": "A dict containing the bump to roughness conversion values: \"factor\", \"normalmap\", \"invert\", \"invertU\", \"invertV\", \"refit\""}
{"id": "ad3a555e7a44a55ef8d9ea45c02f11a1a80059ff8f6afa5b7da8291910af091f", "item_id": "5314035cd6:77", "text": "mipfilter"}
{"id": "3e0fa975f945d8d269370ca03f87a4b775f6634977881ed0e09fed0fe8bd68dd", "item_id": "5314035cd6:78", "text": "The resizing filter used to create MIP levels. Same as texture_filter."}
{"id": "6c621d1a05138a7888d37d9269a9da8e2e11e4aced2f6cfd24b05ab1b9e61bb0", "item_id": "5314035cd6:79", "text": "rules"}
{"id": "75211df16c79768123f2c9a3a16a255259ce293d53b380db9d8cbf4cf8ab1381", "item_id": "5314035cd6:80", "text": "Rules are Python strings that should evaluate to True or False."}
{"id": "ef16849d2e6c3dd777122e1ef16fcef6b86619e01e7365c4147ed4bafad686ab", "item_id": "5314035cd6:81", "text": "All rules are evaluated in the file's order"}
{"id": "556a16022d6d9bc3651508a787f9b8923117c71e568466ede31e991941b6b668", "item_id": "5314035cd6:82", "text": "to modify the args dict. You can add a"}
{"id": "9b3f6837dc77e29ea802011ad98f1264b9d71288d1c987b9b90f6d1e1aecb7eb", "item_id": "5314035cd6:83", "text": "entry in your rule if you want to skip the following rules when the rule is True."}
{"id": "176c21980756c8370008544af2072817b4a2e885fd261ea77c642e3fe108ee9a", "item_id": "5314035cd6:84", "text": "They can the following contain substitution tokens:"}
{"id": "750bff250dabfa0b9ac1417bf060a1fc6db8a2c42b46c509c95268915532355e", "item_id": "5314035cd6:85", "text": "node_type"}
{"id": "9bc5151f9e6656d3fdf08a01ba85c18571c8f9a0629f3775e9bf8e11f594bc6a", "item_id": "5314035cd6:86", "text": "PxrTexture, PxrDomeLight, etc"}
{"id": "9f0c8aa526579f4dbde02f70f4cdf635a22df7d844ce012de5791febea95e732", "item_id": "5314035cd6:87", "text": "classification"}
{"id": "5f0008299869421928bb32bb75d9df79bf2a708a3ff15be62f52e8b0c26afe8d", "item_id": "5314035cd6:88", "text": "bxdf, pattern, light, lightfilter, etc"}
{"id": "39972f837068a11aa58e576c351c603cb40b78715805a64d92dc6faef97ec049", "item_id": "5314035cd6:89", "text": "img_name"}
{"id": "23dba6e64398bd7fb86a9423ea63846747cd58bf567efe5ff63c2ef458ad96cd", "item_id": "5314035cd6:90", "text": "The image name without its extension"}
{"id": "6a8630ca1747874a1844ed92debcc41078a655945e37768975c182eb33ae14dd", "item_id": "5314035cd6:91", "text": "img_ext"}
{"id": "c3b217b90a4b5447105c01d21647c4ae93085d316c33d00f30e6cb792650c4ca", "item_id": "5314035cd6:92", "text": "The image's extension"}
{"id": "4a8a7e27d405793f8d36c087afb4bf40af8588f99f9181d420327ea900065794", "item_id": "5314035cd6:93", "text": "img_atlas"}
{"id": "f13eb067acece7de662228502bdaa588e30043b6ac6a078c5896419609e5b3c3", "item_id": "5314035cd6:94", "text": "True if a texture atlas"}
{"id": "d6608e96f76759d1981cae3915d3dded7457b78316af05d5a2fc708f6b400694", "item_id": "5314035cd6:95", "text": "img_type"}
{"id": "21f2accd8f8e1b43e2f9d8651ba96f08a1109738642c1e2b913aff6fd6e704ef", "item_id": "5314035cd6:96", "text": "'int' or 'float'"}
{"id": "1cce4f341e8a038355a7b3a1ee554687ac8aa80731dede0f8f749fc2dc9043ec", "item_id": "5314035cd6:97", "text": "img_depth"}
{"id": "552023ab41b7a2642148d9e8ab5118564b47015c5df6790851e2b2aa4320151d", "item_id": "5314035cd6:98", "text": "8, 16 or 32"}
{"id": "1e7c2f478fa1b8faff341ebc0500b16f6f2c67ceb8f9d1cccd05a4ed45c47354", "item_id": "5314035cd6:99", "text": "img_nchan"}
{"id": "a75a326e5ca580f95b52bc2438ace9c71dd3b8934d3bd72696bbdca57281ac84", "item_id": "5314035cd6:100", "text": "the number of channels in the image"}
{"id": "0adac98752b71412f5efc6376edc29ce612b0d4822df89cb24c58229bac681af", "item_id": "5314035cd6:101", "text": "ocioconfig"}
{"id": "4bfc6ba9c2c8494b470db57875eba79abf652bc119ac0348b026daa386a2f404", "item_id": "5314035cd6:102", "text": "full path of OCIO config"}
{"id": "8a77f4247a78c57324f314a63912e201039bfec463dbb41b9fad47130ba5232c", "item_id": "5314035cd6:103", "text": "ocioconfig_name"}
{"id": "fbcda480c17a1d275e9acf6cefd5b1c96cc127053645804a5319cf50062777eb", "item_id": "5314035cd6:104", "text": "name of OCIO config: 'basic', 'ACES-1.2', etc"}
{"id": "b334164e87562cb36adbafb8884d696c71c685b2ecf2569c7f40d2e561f7b26d", "item_id": "5314035cd6:105", "text": "For the ACES colorspace to be applied correctly to lights, your rendering role must be named (or aliased) as \"ACES - ACEScg\" or \"ACEScg\". Additionally, RenderMan relies on luma coefficients defined in OCIO configs. These are deprecated in OCIO v2 and may be incorrect in the default ACES config."}
